channel.title: Is this Monero or Whonix error ?
channel.description:
I installed Monero GUI using guide from DOCS, I tred changing nodes and I reinstall Monero(I delete the folder and try to do all steps following the instructions)
7f84e8f84700 WARN net.dns src/common/dns_utils.cpp:508 WARNING: no two valid MoneroPulse DNS checkpoint records were received ERROR default src/wallet/api/utils.cpp:46 error: resolve: Host not found (non-authoritative), try again later
I cant post full LOGS. It says new users can post only 5 links per post. I think that is because editor think utils.cpp is link
Why I'm getting this ? It's Whonix error or I should go ask about it on Monero forum ?
